\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6909549 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6883735\charrsid16386455 Nearby this one. Yes, Nearby, yes. Bungalow you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4600328 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6883735\charrsid16386455 And you're a bachelor?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6909549 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6883735\charrsid16386455 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4600328 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6883735\charrsid16386455 You never }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8134313 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6883735\charrsid16386455 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6909549 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6883735\charrsid16386455 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4600328 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6883735\charrsid16386455 What year were you born?
