\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6909549 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6883735\charrsid16386455 Meals? Downstairs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4600328 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6883735\charrsid16386455 In the kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6909549 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6883735\charrsid16386455 No, in the living room, yes. No, I tell you the kitchen was full up with - kindling wood and that}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7173125\charrsid16386455 \rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6883735\charrsid16386455  where we used to wash of a daytime of a morning and one thing and another.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4600328 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6883735\charrsid16386455 But you would cook in the kitchen?
