\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6909549 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6883735\charrsid16386455 Very nice - yes. I don't know whether it was made hot - I expect it 
