\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6909549 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6883735\charrsid16386455 I don't know what he charged - he charged for it you know. He'd charge.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4600328 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6883735\charrsid16386455 Did she use his oven for anything else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6909549 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6883735\charrsid16386455 The baker. Well if - if mother had a big cake or - a big - pie or anything, a big plum pie because we used to hav
e a big - for about eight of us you know. They used to cook it and we used to go up for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4600328 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6883735\charrsid16386455 That's another errand that you'd run for her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6909549 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6883735\charrsid16386455 Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4600328 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6883735\charrsid16386455 Did she make her own jam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6909549 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6883735\charrsid16386455 Yes. Yes. All kinds of jam.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4600328 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6883735\charrsid16386455 From fruit from the garden?
