Fruit from the garden - gooseberries, currants, black, white, red, rhubarb. Pumpkin - pumpkin jam. That's made something like marmalade - pumpkin.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4600328 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6883735\charrsid16386455 Your father grew pumpkins?
