Yes, at that time. I was at a party last night - at - at Harwich and I told 'em - 'course they had a drink for the toast well I had a - a small bottle of - of - giner - ginger - ginger ale. S}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7173125\charrsid16386455 
c}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6883735\charrsid16386455 hweppes. And I told 'em then I'd been eighty-eight years and 
never touched it. And done twenty-four years in the Navy I did, and however did you. And me oldest brother was older than me you see. When he died I mean to say, he never touched it.
