Oh yes, yes, yes. Yes, in the next door they'd got a - there was the four cottages - there was the four cottages belonging to the one farmer you see. Well there was one wash house for the whole four and there was a - a washing cop
per and a brewing copper and - one of the men used to make a - make the home made brewer for all the farm workers. They used to - the farmer used to provide the mal and hops you see and this man used to make it - with - in the copper.
